													</div>

													<h4>Notes</h4>

													<p>Defender #4 draws to green, defender #3 takes away blue, defender #1 takes away yellow. Relay back to red then teal to look for the shot.</p>

												</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>

								</tab>

								<tab>

									<tab-heading>Left Side One-T</tab-heading>

									<table class="table table-bordered no-top">
										<tbody>
